Package com.risk.model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ILand
    This class represents an interface for continent and country classes This is an interface that continents and countries implement it
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Attack
    this class simulate the attack phase
    Card
    this class represent a card it has properties such as id, name, playerId
    CardExchange
    this class provides an observable object for exchange view it shows the vards of hand and its change
    Console  
    Continent
    This class represents a continent it maintains name, id, control number and playerId it has different methods to change the state of the object
    Country
    This class represents a country it maintains name, id,army, and coordinates of the country it has different methods to change the state and returns the state of the object
    Dice
    this class simulate the dice it has method to roll dice
    Edge
    This class represents a connection between two countries it maintains id of two countries which are neighbor it has different methods to change and set the state of the object
    FactoryLand
    This class constructs objects of continent and country classes
    GameBoard
    This class represents the game board as a singleton it maintains the list of players as well as the map it provides all objects and methods needed for presentation the game
    Land
    This class represents the base class for continent and country class it maintains id and name properties
    Map
    This is a high level class which contains continents and countries it manages most of the tasks regarding these classes, it hase several properties such as name, lands which is the collection of both countries and continents as well as connectivities which in this application is known as edge
    PhaseViewObserver
    this class represents observer for the phase view
    Player
    This class represents a player it maintains id and name of the player also it has different methods to change the status of the object
    TurnOrganizer
    This class maintains the turn and phase status
    WorldDominationObserver
    this class represents a class to show world domination percentage it uses map observable to show the percentage
